ubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 02:15:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/11/for-the-100th-anniversary-of-the-sat-a-look-at-standardized-test-scores-over-time/</guid></item><item><title>2026 年，超过一半的州将承认六月节为法定假日</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/11/more-than-half-of-states-will-recognize-juneteenth-as-a-legal-holiday-in-2026/</link><description>今年，至少有 33 个州和哥伦比亚特区将在法律上承认六月节为公共假期。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jun 2026 02:00:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/11/more-than-half-of-states-will-recognize-juneteenth-as-a-legal-holiday-in-2026/</guid></item><item><title>与其他高收入国家的人们相比，美国人对其民主制度的运作方式更加不满意</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/10/americans-are-more-dissatisfied-with-how-their-democracy-is-working-than-people-in-other-high-income-countries/</link><description>绝大多数民主党人（86%）对美国民主的运作方式不满意。大约一半的共和党人（51%）也这么说。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 02:31:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/10/americans-are-more-dissatisfied-with-how-their-democracy-is-working-than-people-in-other-high-income-countries/</guid></item><item><title>超越红与蓝：政治类型学</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/politics/2026/06/10/beyond-red-vs-blue-the-political-typology/</link><description>我们的分类法根据公众的政治和文化价值观，而不是他们的政党，将他们分为九个群体——用远远不止两种颜色来描绘美国政治的图景。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 02:01:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/politics/2026/06/10/beyond-red-vs-blue-the-political-typology/</guid></item><item><title>政治类型学 2026</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/politics/quiz/political-typology/</link><description>参加我们的测验，看看我们的九个政治类型组中哪一个最适合您。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 01:46:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/politics/quiz/political-typology/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普已年满 80 岁，谁是现任世界领导人中最年长和最年轻的？</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/09/as-trump-turns-80-who-are-the-oldest-and-youngest-current-world-leaders/</link><description>随着特朗普年满 80 岁，186 名国家领导人中只有 16 人年龄更大。领导人年龄中位数为 63 岁，尼泊尔总理 36 岁，是最年轻的。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 02:08:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/short-reads/2026/06/09/as-trump-turns-80-who-are-the-oldest-and-youngest-current-world-leaders/</guid></item><item><title>以色列人、巴勒斯坦人、美国人对伊朗战争有不同看法</title><link>https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/06/09/israelis-palestinians-americans-see-war-in-iran-differently/</link><description>四分之三的以色列人认为美国在攻击伊朗方面做出了正确的决定，而十分之八的巴勒斯坦人则持相反观点。美国人的分歧更大。由 PolitePaul 服务提供</description><pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 14:24:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.pewresearch.org/global/2026/06/09/israelis-palestinians-americans-see-war-in-iran-differently/</guid></item></channel></rss>